# DevConnect 

DevConnect is a React + Redux-powered task and team management platform for developers. It allows users to create, manage, and persist cards (features/tasks) with a responsive, modern UI built using Tailwind CSS.

---

##  Features

- 🗃️ Add new task/feature cards with a title and description
- 💾 Data persistence using localStorage
- 🔁 Multi-page routing with React Router (`Home`, `About`, `Features`)
- 🎯 Global state management using Redux Toolkit
- 🎨 Styled using Tailwind CSS for responsive UI

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- [React](https://reactjs.org/)
- [Redux Toolkit](https://redux-toolkit.js.org/)
- [React Redux](https://react-redux.js.org/)
- [React Router](https://reactrouter.com/)
- [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)
- [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/) – for faster build & dev experience

---
